sion - ICOQuest.com\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"ts to us, please read our following guest posting guidelines: You guest posting article must have unique contents, with good English and grammar. Your guest posting article must be related to cryptocurrency and blockchain. Your guest post must be at least 600 words long. If your are interested in writing for us, please contact us to discuss the pos\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Active write-for-us page with clear guidelines on submitting cryptocurrency and blockchain content.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"score\": 6.6,\n      \"domain_authority\": 22,\n      \"dofollow\": true,\n      \"spam_score\": \"low\",\n      \"relevance_score\": 9,\n      \"traffic_estimate\": \"low\",\n      \"freshness_score\": 5,\n      \"contextual_fit\": 8,\n      \"posting_ease\": \"manual_review\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"medium\",\n      \"audit_notes\": \"Focuses on ICOs and blockchain topics. Highly relevant domain for coinography.com that supports dofollow links, though it has moderate traffic and domain authority.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://digitalcryptobox.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"domain\": \"digitalcryptobox.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://digitalcryptobox.com/write-for-us\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Write For Us Cryptocurrency, Blockchain, NFT, ICO, Crypto Tokens\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"rtunities! Write For Us Cryptocurrency Guest Post Guidelines for Cryptocurrency Guest Post Cryptocurrency Guest Post ICO Guest Posting Blockchain Guest Post write for us crypto crypto blog write for us submit crypto guest post write for us + crypto crypto guest post write for us crypto + write for us “crypto” + “write for us” write for us – crypto\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Submit a guest post or article directly through the provided instructions for Crypto, NFTs, and DeFi.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"score\": 5.5,\n      \"domain_authority\": 18,\n      \"dofollow\": true,\n      \"spam_score\": \"medium\",\n      \"relevance_score\": 8,\n      \"traffic_estimate\": \"low\",\n      \"freshness_score\": 5,\n      \"contextual_fit\": 7,\n      \"posting_ease\": \"manual_review\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"low\",\n      \"audit_notes\": \"Though relevant to the cryptocurrency niche, the guidelines page uses keyword stuffing footprints, raising the spam profile slightly.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"domain\": \"kryptomoney.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.kryptomoney.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"Submit Guest Post - Latest Crypto News advertisement [email&#160;protected] Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com --> Submit Press Release Submit Guest Post Write for Kryptomoney.com News Bitcoin News Blockchain News Cryptocurrency News Ethereum News Exchanges News Regulations News Price Analysis Bitcoin (BTC) Analysis Et\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Dedicated submission form and guidelines for contributors working in the cryptocurrency and blockchain field.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"score\": 8.2,\n      \"domain_authority\": 45,\n      \"dofollow\": true,\n      \"spam_score\": \"low\",\n      \"relevance_score\": 9.5,\n      \"traffic_estimate\": \"medium\",\n      \"freshness_score\": 6,\n      \"contextual_fit\": 9,\n      \"posting_ease\": \"manual_review\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"high_priority\",\n      \"audit_notes\": \"An established, active cryptocurrency news portal with solid domain authority. Provides highly valuable, relevant links with great visibility for coinography.com.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://icoshock.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"domain\": \"icoshock.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://icoshock.com/submit-guest-post\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Submit a Crypto Guest Post -\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"re that there is a $30 fee for publishing a post. Guidelines for Crypto, ICO, or Blockchain-Related Guest Posts We aim for fresh, exciting content at ICOshock, but it should also be objective. Therefore, all users must familiarize themselves with and follow these guidelines: Ethics : Do not write posts or formulations that are abusive, racist, thre\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"Direct portal to submit a guest article about cryptocurrency, Web3, or new projects.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"outreach_email\",\n      \"score\": 5.8,\n      \"domain_authority\": 20,\n      \"dofollow\": true,\n      \"spam_score\": \"medium\",\n      \"relevance_score\": 8.5,\n      \"traffic_estimate\": \"low\",\n      \"freshness_score\": 5,\n      \"contextual_fit\": 8,\n      \"posting_ease\": \"manual_review\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"low\",\n      \"audit_notes\": \"Charges a flat $30 publication fee. While the niche fit is good, paid links carry a higher risk profile and lower natural organic value.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://cryptoslate.com/directory\",\n      \"domain\": \"cryptoslate.com\",\n      \"type\": \"directory\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://cryptoslate.com/directory\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Crypto Directory: Companies, Products &amp; People | CryptoSlate\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"6 Open law profile Philippines SEC CASP Rules and Guidelines (2025) Effective Philippines SEC Memorandum Circular Nos. 04 and 05, Series of 2025 establish the CASP Rules and Guidelines for... Jun 8, 2026 Open law profile Vietnam Law on Digital Technology Industry: Digital-Asset Provisions Effective Vietnam’s Law 71/2025/QH15 defines digital assets,\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"A highly authority crypto news directory where projects and companies can be submitted for inclusion.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"submit_listing\",\n      \"score\": 8.7,\n      \"domain_authority\": 78,\n      \"dofollow\": false,\n      \"spam_score\": \"low\",\n      \"relevance_score\": 10,\n      \"traffic_estimate\": \"high\",\n      \"freshness_score\": 8,\n      \"contextual_fit\": 9.5,\n      \"posting_ease\": \"account_needed\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"high_priority\",\n      \"audit_notes\": \"CryptoSlate is an extremely authoritative and trusted brand directory in the crypto industry. Recommended for massive referral traffic and credibility boost.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cryptosdirectory.com/join\",\n      \"domain\": \"cryptosdirectory.com\",\n      \"type\": \"directory\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptosdirectory.com/join\",\n      \"target_title\": \"Untitled\",\n      \"target_excerpt\": \"\",\n      \"opportunity_context\": \"A curated directory specifically for cryptocurrency services, tools, and platforms.\",\n      \"opportunity_freshness\": \"evergreen\",\n      \"posting_action\": \"submit_listing\",\n      \"score\": 6.2,\n      \"domain_authority\": 15,\n      \"dofollow\": true,\n      \"spam_score\": \"low\",\n      \"relevance_score\": 9,\n      \"traffic_estimate\": \"low\",\n      \"freshness_score\": 4,\n      \"contextual_fit\": 8,\n      \"posting_ease\": \"easy_form\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"medium\",\n      \"audit_notes\": \"Dedicated directory for cryptocurrency tools and websites. Straightforward form-based submission with solid direct niche relevance.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780985244335}}
